reviewText: This video is from a training Gottman did. It has a wealth of information.  The handout was disappointing, it is one page and is the house analogy he uses but with very basic detail.  I would have preferred more detailed references and information from the research he quoted. Despite the lack of handouts, references, ect. the message was a food clinical overview of marriage research and relationship dynamics.  Geared toward mental health professionals.
